data.description: Welcome Home to this 2-Story home that features 4 BR/2.5 BA and features an amazing spacious floor plan.  The main level features an open Foyer, formal living room, dining room, kitchen, sunroom, half bath, and a gas fireplace in the family room.  A laundry room is located on the main level next to the two-car garage.  Upstairs includes the Master Bedroom with an on-suite Bathroom with a separate Garden Tub & Shower, 3 additional bedrooms, 1 additional bathroom located in the hallway.  The home has a deck area located back of the home great for entertaining family/friends.  Amenities for homeowners: pool and tennis court areas.  Speaking of accessible, all the shopping and restaurants you could wish for is just minutes away and easy access to I-20.    SOLD AS IS WITH RIGHTS TO INSPECTION.
